Apollo 11 Mission
The Apollo 11 mission is a historical event related to space exploration.

Neil Armstrong
Neil Armstrong was the commander of the Apollo 11 mission.

Buzz Aldrin
Buzz Aldrin was a member of the Apollo 11 mission crew alongside Neil Armstrong.

Michael Collins
Michael Collins was the command module pilot of the Apollo 11 mission.

Tranquility Base
Tranquility Base is where the Apollo 11 lunar module landed.

The command module 'Columbia' orbited the Moon during the Apollo 11 mission.
